column5: can any of you guys tell me what the ice is like on rosseau if there is any

Lake Muskoka froze all the way only yesterday. South east end anyway. When I went to work in the morning it was still open, and by early afternoon she was froze. From my work I can see across a stretch probably for almost 2 miles. So at the max. there is probably an inch. Small bays may be different but I wouldn't go out there yet.  Rosseau won't be any different.  Definitely not good ice yet...   Hookset.
